{"word":"ἐπιτομή","slug":"ἐπιτομή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιτομή</b></el> <el>(ἐπιτομή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐπιτέμνω'><el>ἐπιτέμνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a cutting on the surface, incision</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an epitome, abridgment</i>, <b><a href='S:Cicero, M. Tullius'>Cic.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}